"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1931319-olympics-greg-rutherford-health-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Greg had previously disclosed the severity of his injury, stating he had \\\"effectively [given himself] a C-section\\\" after tearing his abdominal muscles in a dramatic slide through the legs of professional skaters Brendyn Hatfield and Colin Grafton.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Grafton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Colin Grafton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Grafton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colin_Grafton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympian Greg Rutherford has recounted a 'terrifying' and 'harrowing' ordeal from last month when a skylight in his home unexpectedly exploded, sending shards of glass flying into his living room.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999964993549, \"rank\": 3.4616336508427507e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Rutherford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.85275678485603e-33, \"text\": \"Greg Rutherford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Rutherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Rutherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He shared the chilling aftermath on social media, revealing how he was left 'shaking' after the incident, which occurred just moments after his children had been sitting underneath the skylight.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From his home, he recounted: \\\"One of the most terrifying experiences - one of our skylights up here just exploded.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just, literally, me standing in the kitchen watching the TV on the wall, and it just went - bang!\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And glass went everywhere.\\\"\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic heroGreg Rutherfordhas been struck down by a severe bout of food poisoning during his time in Paris, leaving him bedridden and in a \\\"horrendously bad way.\\\"\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3342227426129028e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37 year old athlete-turned-presenter shared a candid video from his sickbed after recording an episode of the Inside Track podcast with Sanya Richi Ross, revealing the extent of his illness.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the clip, a visibly unwell Greg explains: \\\"Hello everyone.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thought I'd give you a little update.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have just recorded the first pod with Sonya, really good fun.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sonya_Rebecchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.658395276917132e-19, \"text\": \"Sonya\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sonya_Rebecchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sonya_Rebecchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I got food poisoning last night.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been in a horrendously bad way and I have not felt this unwell in a long time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued, detailing his distressing symptoms: \\\"I have been puking, like violently projectile vomiting, not to get really in depth with everybody.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Day one in Paris has been me laying on my bed, getting up recording the first show, and I am now back in bed before we record another show in two hours time.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3342227426129028e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"God food poisioning is horrendous.\\\"\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This setback comes after a tough year for the retired Olympic champion, who had to pull out of Dancing on Ice just shy of the final due to a significant injury, reportsthe Mirror.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Do not miss:Team GB seal Olympic gold as Emily Craig and Imogen Grant win in double sculls  Do not miss:Piers Morgan says 'all trans women athletes should be banned' from Olympics  Do not miss:Olympic swimmer collapses and given oxygen before being taken away on stretcher  He further explained the close call involving his son, saying: \\\"I kid you not, two minutes before, Milo was down here doing some school work, and I said, 'It's a nice day, go out on the deck, mate.'\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2353, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emily Craig\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\"}, {\"begin\": 2369, \"end\": 2381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imogen_Grant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imogen Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imogen_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imogen_Grant\"}, {\"begin\": 2416, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piers_Morgan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Piers Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piers_Morgan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piers_Morgan\"}, {\"begin\": 2685, \"end\": 2689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titus_Annius_Milo\", \"score\": 0.999999962829407, \"rank\": 3.717075793073422e-08, \"text\": \"Milo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titus_Annius_Milo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titus_Annius_Milo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank God I did that because if not, I can not even imagine what could have happened.\\\"\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a turn of events earlier this year,Greg's competitor on the ice, Ryan Thomas, emerged victorious in the 2024 series.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Thomas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2183259989763893e-26, \"text\": \"Ryan Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a touching gesture during his victory speech, Thomas honoured Rutherford, who had led the leaderboard until misfortune hit.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3042, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.999043579042414, \"rank\": 0.0009573265974914811, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 3058, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Rutherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999331530511, \"rank\": 6.667231063919588e-08, \"text\": \"Rutherford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Rutherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Rutherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutherford warmly congratulated the ex-Coronation Streetstar on his impressive triumph, stating: \\\"Well done, brother, I am glad I have got a friend for life in you,\\\" and acknowledged: \\\"He's had his fair share of ups and downs during his process, so to come out winning is utterly spectacular.\\\"\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3121, \"end\": 3131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Rutherford\", \"score\": 0.9999999331530511, \"rank\": 6.667231063919588e-08, \"text\": \"Rutherford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Rutherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Rutherford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before hanging up his spikes in 2018 due to an ankle injury, Greg Rutherford clinched a gold medal in the long jump at the London 2012 Olympics and bagged a bronze at the Rio de Janeiro Games in 2016.\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Rutherford\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.85275678485603e-33, \"text\": \"Greg Rutherford\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Rutherford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Rutherford\"}, {\"begin\": 3539, \"end\": 3559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2602362454610483e-13, \"text\": \"London 2012 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3587, \"end\": 3601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.245629974210533e-16, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3755, \"end\": 3768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.70122224307254e-27, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3804, \"end\": 3817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.